<div class="flex-grow w-5/12 p-6">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 mb-6">Service Assignments</h1>
    <p>Service Assignments in ToolKeeper are essential for tracking where tools are located and what jobs, employees, or
        stockrooms they’re assigned to. This feature ensures accountability and efficient resource management across
        jobs, vehicles, and employees.</p>

    <h2 class="space-y-8 text-lg">Service Assignment Fields</h2>
    <div class="text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 mb-4">
        <p>Each Service Assignment (SA) includes several fields, both required and optional, to provide detailed
            tracking. Here’s an overview of each field:</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-1">
        <div>
            <h3 class="text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-300 text-lg font-semibold">ID</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-300">Unique identifier for each SA, auto-generated by ToolKeeper.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h3 class="text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-300 text-lg font-semibold">Job Number</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-300">Required, unique identifier for each assignment within the
                tenant.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h3 class="text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-300 text-lg font-semibold">Job Name</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-300">Optional descriptive name for the job or assignment.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h3 class="text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-300 text-lg font-semibold">Type</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-300">Specifies the assignment type (e.g., Jobsite, Stockroom,
                Employee).</p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h3 class=" text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-300 text-lg font-semibold">Active</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-300">Boolean flag for active status (default: true).</p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h3 class="text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-300 text-lg font-semibold">Phone</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-300">Optional contact number associated with the assignment.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h3 class="text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-300 text-lg font-semibold">Notes</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-300">Optional notes for additional details about the assignment.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h3 class=" text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-300 text-lg font-semibold">Tenant</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-300">Tenant reference, linking the SA to a specific tenant.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-300 text-lg font-semibold">Timestamps</h2>
    <p>Each SA records timestamps for:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-300">
        <li class="text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-300"><strong>Created At:</strong> When the assignment was created.</li>
        <li class="text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-300"><strong>Updated At:</strong> When the assignment was last updated.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-300 text-lg font-semibold">Service Assignment Indexing</h2>
    <p class="text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-300">ToolKeeper indexes the <code>jobNumber</code> field with the <code>tenant</code> field to ensure unique job
        numbers within each tenant, supporting multi-tenant usage.</p>

    <h2 class="text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-300 text-lg font-semibold">Managing Service Assignments</h2>
    <p class="text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-300">ToolKeeper’s search and filter features allow you to easily locate assignments by job number, job name, type, and
        tenant. By utilizing Service Assignments, ToolKeeper keeps every tool accounted for, ensuring an efficient
        workflow across projects and personnel.</p>
</div>